name: died in the Meta-
description:
We are living a life under a Drive, no need the oxygen because evolution only kill the gene. 

Flesh can be replaced, and bones growth by the cable. Biology is superficial and intelligence is artificial, the genesis isn’t on the bible, if Metaverse can clone a gene.

Unplugged it, extinction it. 

If our soul only formed by the number of currency, and all the token rebuild the Paradise.

So, what will happen if we die in the Meta-?
